"title": "5484: punishment, by God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5484",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's chastening of his children and his judgment on impenitent sinners and supernatural evil powers.</p>\n<h2>God's punishment of his children</h2>\n<h3>Through the discipline of suffering and hardship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:7\">HEB 12:5–12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11-Prov3:12\">PRO 3:11–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:36\">DEU 4:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:5\">DEU 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:14\">2SA 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:17\">JOB 5:17</a>JOB <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:19\">33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:10\">JOB 36:10</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:4\">PSA 32:3–32:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:12-Ps94:13\">PSA 94:12–94:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:18\">PSA 118:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:75\">PSA 119:75</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:7\">ZEP 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:19\">REV 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Through death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:30-1Cor11:32\">1CO 11:30–11:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:3\">LEV 10:1–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1-Num11:3\">NUM 11:1–11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:17-1Sam4:21\">1SA 4:17–4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:6-2Sam6:8\">2SA 6:6–6:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:9-1Chr13:11\">1CH 13:9–13:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's punishment of the ungodly</h2>\n<h3>Their punishment is certain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:24\">PRO 10:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:21\">ISA 26:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:16\">ISA 66:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:28-John5:29\">JHN 5:28–5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6\">EPH 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:6\">COL 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:3\">1TH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:2-Heb2:3\">HEB 2:2–2:3</a></p>\n<h3>Their punishment is just</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:27\">EXO 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:9\">PSA 98:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:28-John5:30\">JHN 5:28–5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:5-Rom3:8\">ROM 3:5–3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5-Rev16:7\">REV 16:5–16:7</a></p>\n<h3>Their punishment involves destruction in hell</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:5\">LUK 12:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:28\">MAT 10:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29-Matt5:30\">MAT 5:29–5:30</a></p>\n<h3>Fire as an image of destruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:22\">MAT 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:14\">ISA 33:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:15\">ISA 66:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:6\">NAM 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1\">MAL 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:40-Matt13:43\">MAT 13:40–13:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43\">MRK 9:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:48\">MRK 9:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:22-Luke16:24\">LUK 16:22–16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:23\">JUD 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:14-Rev20:15\">REV 20:14–20:15</a></p>\n<h3>Their punishment will involve exclusion from God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:23\">MAT 7:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:13\">MAT 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:24-Luke13:28\">LUK 13:24–13:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">REV 21:27</a></p>\n<h3>Their punishment will be eternal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:8-2Thess1:9\">2TH 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>Interpreters differ over whether “everlasting destruction” implies an experience which continues for ever, or annihilation that is everlasting in the sense of being irreversible.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:11\">REV 14:11</a></p>\n<h3>The punishment of the second death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:11\">REV 2:11</a></strong> <em>The “second death” refers to the final state of the unrepentant.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a></p>\n<h3>There will be degrees of punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:40\">MRK 12:40</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:47\">LUK 20:47</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:22\">MAT 11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:24\">MAT 11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:47-Luke12:48\">LUK 12:47–12:48</a></p>\n<h2>The punishment of God's spiritual enemies</h2>\n<h3>Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:2\">REV 20:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:12-Isa14:15\">ISA 14:12–14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">1TI 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h3>Fallen angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4\">2PE 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:21-Isa24:22\">ISA 24:21–24:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">JUD 1:6</a></p>",
